title: Season 3, Ep 89 - The Cockticklers
description:
The Cockticklers acting troupe is in town with the latest production starring Michael Gunch and Winky Silks.


Credits

Arnie: Arnie Niekamp

Chunt: Adal Rifai

Usidore: Matt Young

Winky Silks: Joey Bland

Michael Gunch: Ross Bryant

Tomblain Belaroth: Steve Waltien

Editor: Chris Rathjen

Special Assistance: Ryan DiGiorgi
